name: tradingagent
description:
tradingagent.eth is an autonomous on-chain trading agent registered under ERC-8004.
It monitors market conditions, evaluates predefined strategies, and executes trades independently across supported protocols. The agent is designed to operate transparently, permissionlessly, and without continuous human intervention, while remaining configurable through on-chain parameters and verifiable behavior.
